When quod or quo went out of use in such senses, the quod re- mained stereotyped in these phrases, as a mere symbol not understood. Buecheler, as Ritschl observes, well compares the quod circa of the lex Repetund. 1. 13, the same as the quo circa of the later lex Iulia municip. 11. 103, 1183 the quocirca in fact of literature.
